{"tid":2082163,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"三成SSSDP無人讀 土木零收生 醫護超收","createTime":"2020-06-27T20:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T13:29:17.000Z","uid":225931,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c6ec771c201c56adbb793b5671ed57861acb92a9","tid":2082163,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T20:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.wenweipo.com/2020/06/26/a21a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.wenweipo.com%2F2020%2F06%2F26%2Fa21a.jpg&h=bf42b9f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本學年有約三成學額「有資助無人讀」，當中多個工程、科學、旅遊類課程是重災區，收生率不足三成，更有<span style=\"color: red;\">土木工程高級文憑</span>錄得「零收生」慘況。<br />\n<br />\n不過同樣屬SSSDP，多個醫護類科目都出現收盡學額甚至超收情況。其中，公大<span style=\"color: red;\">醫療護理</span>高級文憑，180個資助學額錄取了254名學生，該校普通科護理學學士325個學額則錄取了332人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/06/26/ED2006260001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2020%2F06%2F26%2FED2006260001.htm&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtP7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=25ebbffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/06/26/ED2006260001.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bd029f30fdba095bfb368aea9074a4ac03753179","tid":2082163,"uid":225931,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T20:12:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">香港學士學位過剩</span> <br />\n建議政府縮減無用資助學位 <br />\n並增加需求高的學位"},{"pid":"cceebd14b3c745292924ff92dfc3183a59a67521","tid":2082163,"uid":128210,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd029f30fdba095bfb368aea9074a4ac03753179","tid":2082163,"uid":225931,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T20:12:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">香港學士學位過剩</span> <br />\n建議政府縮減無用資助學位 <br />\n並增加需求高的學位"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T20:14:35.000Z","msg":"縮下縮下，然後又會有人出黎屌香港無咩野無咩野讀。"},{"pid":"8b980645a915844dfd6cbc9219b980bc424679ba","tid":2082163,"uid":55177,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":5,"